    <item>
      <title>特朗普征收关税导致美元飙升，股市下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/dollar-surges-stocks-set-to-fall-on-trump-tariffs-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普兑现对加拿大、墨西哥和中国进口产品征收关税的威胁后，美元飙升，而股票市场和数字货币暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/dollar-surges-stocks-set-to-fall-on-trump-tariffs-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 22:25:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度回应特朗普 力图摆脱“关税之王”称号</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/shun-protectionism-india-signals-to-industry-with-tariff-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度政府在预算中大幅削减了进口关税，并表示不会利用保护主义措施来庇护企业，这显然是为了阻止美国总统唐纳德·特朗普与其主要合作伙伴发动新一轮贸易战的报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/shun-protectionism-india-signals-to-industry-with-tariff-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 12:16:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
